OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772935393
OL,3,CIrish actress Jessie Buckley reveals
OL,4,Cbattle with eating disorder and
OL,5,Cdepression
OL,7,FIrish actress Jessie Buckley has
OL,8,Frevealed she went through a battle
OL,9,Fwith an eating disorder and depression
OL,10,Fduring her teenage years.
OL,12,FThe 36-year-old from Killarney, County
OL,13,FKerry, credited a love of music and
OL,14,Ftheatre for helping her with her
OL,15,Frecovery, but did not specify which
OL,16,Feating disorder she had.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
