PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772935393
OL,3,CIrish actress Jessie Buckley reveals
OL,4,Cbattle with eating disorder and
OL,5,Cdepression
OL,7,FShe told Lauren Laverne on BBC Radio
OL,8,F4's Desert Island Discs: "I had an
OL,9,Feating disorder, and it took time, and
OL,10,Fit took a lot of help, and also it was
OL,11,Fdepression...
OL,13,F"I didn't know how to be alive the way
OL,14,FI wanted to be, and it was difficult,
OL,15,Fbut I do not for a second regret it,
OL,16,Fand I think I've been able to
OL,17,Ftransform it and recognise our
OL,18,Fvulnerabilities as humans in the world.
OL,26,@pD@ZOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772935393
OL,3,CIrish actress Jessie Buckley reveals
OL,4,Cbattle with eating disorder and
OL,5,Cdepression
OL,7,F"You know, you can't walk through life
OL,8,Fnot being affected, but you can
OL,9,Ftransform that into something that
OL,10,Fallows you to be more human and alive
OL,11,Fin the way that you want to be.
OL,13,F"And I'm very grateful for everybody
OL,14,Fwho helped me along the way with that,
OL,15,Fand for the people who held space for
OL,16,Fthat...
OL,18,F"I've been in therapy since I was 17,
OL,19,FI still go every week."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUzD@AOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
