OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772935393
OL,3,CIrish actress Jessie Buckley reveals
OL,4,Cbattle with eating disorder and
OL,5,Cdepression
OL,7,FBuckley has recently received a string
OL,8,Fof awards for her performance as
OL,9,FWilliam Shakespeare's wife Agnes
OL,10,FHathaway, historically known as Anne,
OL,11,Fin the film adaptation of Maggie
OL,12,FO'Farrell's novel Hamnet.
OL,14,FThe actress also said she realised
OL,15,Facting was "essential" for her
OL,16,Fwellbeing and "like water to me" after
OL,17,Fher appendix "almost burst" during one
OL,18,Fof her earliest performances and she
OL,19,Frefused to leave until the play was
OL,20,Ffinished, when she was then taken to
OL,21,Fhospital.
OL,26,@wD@LOUwD@VO]xD@OOUxD@`O]yD@NOUyD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
