OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772935393
OL,3,CIrish actress Jessie Buckley reveals
OL,4,Cbattle with eating disorder and
OL,5,Cdepression
OL,7,FShe continued: "When I moved to
OL,8,FLondon, I still wasn't out of the
OL,9,Fwoods.
OL,11,F"I think there were moments where I
OL,12,Fwas like, 'if I don't get better here,
OL,13,Fthis music, this being part of theatre
OL,14,F` I'm not going to be able to do this
OL,15,Fany more, and I probably won't
OL,16,Fsurvive'.
OL,18,F"And that was the thing that turned it
OL,19,Fin my head, I was like, 'I don't want
OL,20,Fto sacrifice that, this is bigger than
OL,21,Fthat', and won."
OL,26,@oD@POUsD@AOUzD@AOU}D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
