OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772935393
OL,3,CIrish actress Jessie Buckley reveals
OL,4,Cbattle with eating disorder and
OL,5,Cdepression
OL,7,FBuckley also recounted her time on BBC
OL,8,Ftalent show I'd Do Anything, which was
OL,9,Fabout the search for an actress to
OL,10,Fplay Nancy in a West End production of
OL,11,FOliver!, and which catapulted her to
OL,12,Ffame.
OL,14,FIn an interview with British Vogue in
OL,15,FJanuary, she spoke about being
OL,16,Fcriticised for her appearance during
OL,17,Fher time on the show.
OL,19,FSpeaking to Laverne, Buckley said: "I
OL,20,Fdon't like that part of it.
OL,26,@{D@dOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772935393
OL,3,CIrish actress Jessie Buckley reveals
OL,4,Cbattle with eating disorder and
OL,5,Cdepression
OL,7,F"I think that was a young woman who's
OL,8,Ftrying to discover her body and
OL,9,Fherself, like we all do. And I wish
OL,10,Fthat hadn't happened.
OL,12,F"I think I was putting a brave face
OL,13,Fon, because really what I wanted to do
OL,14,Fwas sing and I wanted to act, and I
OL,15,Fwanted to be part of this industry,
OL,16,Fand all of a sudden you had to be a
OL,17,Fcertain kind of person.
OL,19,F"And I just wasn't, I never will be.
OL,20,FThat's just not me."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU{D@AOU|D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
