OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772935393
OL,3,CIrish actress Jessie Buckley reveals
OL,4,Cbattle with eating disorder and
OL,5,Cdepression
OL,7,FBuckley added: "I'm so proud of that
OL,8,Fgirl. I think she did great and I
OL,9,Fdon't regret any of it."
OL,11,FShe also spoke about her
OL,12,F"extraordinary" mother, and said: "My
OL,13,Fparents are no longer together, and
OL,14,Fshe lives in Dublin, and she's writing
OL,15,Fher own story right now at 60 years of
OL,16,Fage, and I'm so proud of her."
OL,18,FShe sounded emotional as she gave her
OL,19,Ffirst song choice, which was a
OL,20,Frendition of her mother, Marina,
OL,21,Fsinging O Holy Night in church.
OL,26,@oD@POUqD@XO]tD@AOUtD@OO]tD@cOUxD@^O]
